survey.automatic_detection_helpful_explanation: It's quite a lot of data to analyze. Sometimes you miss an anomaly, and the automatic detector finds them for you. Of course you still have to look around for other anomalies, but if there were a lot, it was a helpful tool.
survey.history_helpful_explanation: I did not always look at the history since I was busy with incoming events. So if I had the time it was helpful
